Hey Franco! It sounds like you're interested in the ClickBank ad credit. Could you please provide more details or specify what you need help with regarding the $500 ClickBank ad credit?
I received an email from clickbank that you were offering a $500 ad credit for new accounts

Got it, Franco! To redeem your $500 ClickBank ad credit, you'll need to follow these steps:
1. Access the Billing Section on admanager.newsbreak.com.
2. Under Ad Credits, click on â€˜Add ad credits.'
3. Choose â€˜Customizeâ€™ and enter the total value of your gifted ad credit, plus at least $1. For example, if your gifted ad credit is $500, your total should be a minimum of $501 or more.
4. Enter the promotional code you received from ClickBank.
5. Provide your credit card information and check out.
For more detailed instructions, you can refer to this article: [How to redeem a NewsBreak ad credit](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/17391456255629-How-to-redeem-a-NewsBreak-ad-credit).
If you have any other questions or need further assistance, feel free to ask!
i didn't receive any coupon from either clickbank and newsbreak

Oh, I see. If you didn't receive a promotional code from ClickBank or NewsBreak, I recommend checking your spam or junk email folders just in case it ended up there. If you still can't find it, you might need to contact ClickBank support to ensure that the email was sent correctly.
If you need further assistance, I can also send an email to our support team on your behalf. Would you like me to do that?
